    Follow along with the tutorials and have a look at the code. Progres from knowing nothing at all to publishing a full game as an indie dev hero.
    </p>
    <h2 class="title is-size-4">So where do I start?</h2>
    <p>
    Start small. Learn basic game development techniques and consepts by building very small manageable games. Here you will find a list of progressively more difficult game projects that we are going to work on during this game development quest. Each project will build on top of the previous consept, reinforcing your understanding and knowledge of game development techniques.
    </p>
    <aside class="aside">
    <h3 class="is-size-5">Resources</h3>
    <a target="_blank" title="Article on GameFromScratch.com" href="https://www.gamefromscratch.com/post/2013/08/01/Just-starting-out-what-games-should-I-make.aspx">
