    </aside>

    <h2 class="title is-size-4">Warning for the eager Knight-errant</h2>
    <p>
    The difficulty of each project on this list may change depending on whether you use a game framework or an engine. For example, building a clone of the game Pong from scratch in a programming language, is much more intimidating than to use for example the Construct 2 game engine (which will only take about 10 minutes to create).
    </p>
    <p>
    On our quest for game dev we will explore frameworks as well as game engines. The main quest is to complete each project progressively using only one framework. Side quests will include developing the same game in different languages, frameworks and engines.
    </p>
